Field Label: Stroop-match-RR: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incm-RR) minus meanRT(conm-RR)
Stroop-nonmatch-RR: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incnm-RR) minus meanRT(connm-RR)
Stroop-match-RS: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incm-RS) minus meanRT(conm-RS)
Stroop-nonmatch-RS: difference RT(msec) = meanRT(incnm-RS) minus meanRT(connm-RS)
Z-score for Stroop-match-RR: difference Z-score = Z(incm-RR) minus Z(conm-RR)
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch-RR: difference Z-score = Z(incnm-RR) minus Z(connm-RR)
Z-score for Stroop-match-RS: difference Z-score = Z(incm-RS) minus Z(conm-RS)
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch-RS: difference Z-score = Z(incnm-RS) minus Z(connm-RS)
Z-score for Stroop-match: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RR + Z-score Stroop-match-RS)/2
Z-score for Stroop-nonmatch: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RR + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2
Z-score for Stroop-RR: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RR + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RR)/2
Z-score for Stroop-RS: mean Z-score = (Z-score Stroop-match-RS + Z-score Stroop-nonmatch-RS)/2

	If 'YES': How often did this occur?

	If 'YES': How often did this occur?

	If 'YES': How often did this occur?

	If 'YES': Can you describe these for me?

In the past week did you experience fatigue, loss of energy, or diffuse aches and pains?

	If 'YES': How often did you experience these feelings?
In the last week have you noticed a change in your desire to work, spend time with others, or engage in other activities in which you would normally participate?

In the last week have you noticed feelings of tension, irritability, an inability to concentrate, or worrying about little things?

	If 'YES': Can you give me an example?

In the last week have you noticed physical symptoms like heartburn, dry mouth, headaches, sweating, or heart palpitations?

	If 'YES': Did you experience these things when you were worrying or thinking about problems you might encounter?

	If 'YES': How much weight did you lose?

	If 'YES': How much weight did you gain?

	If 'YES': Can you give me an example? How often?

	If 'YES': Can you give me an example? How often?

	If 'YES': Can you give me an example? How often?

	If 'YES': Can you give me an example? How often?

TENSION (feelings of tension, fatigue, startle response, moved to tears easily, trembling, restlessness, inability to relax)
FEARS (of dark, strangers, being left alone, animals, traffic, crowds)

Section Header:
In the last week:

	
		Did you have any sleeping problems like difficulty falling asleep, unsatisfying sleep, nightmares, or night terrors?
	
		Did you have trouble concentrating or trying to remember things?
	
		Did you feel down and depressed or feel like you had lost interest in things that you used to enjoy?


	If ANY 'YES': How often did this occur? Did it interfere with your daily functioning?
Field Label: INSOMNIA (difficulty falling asleep, broken sleep, unsatisfying sleep and fatigue on waking, dreams, nightmares, night terrors)
DEPRESSED MOOD (depression, loss of interest, anhedonia in hobbies, early waking, diurnal swing)

Section Header:
In the last week:

	
		Did you experience any pains and aches, twitching, stiffness, or other muscular symptoms?
	
		Did you have any sensory problems such as blurred vision, hot/cold flashes, or feeling weak?
	
		Did you have any cardiovascular symptoms such as chest pains or fainting feelings?


	If ANY 'YES': How often did this occur? Did it interfere with your daily functioning?
Field Label: SOMATIC (MUSCULAR) (pains and aches, twitching, stiffness, myoclonic jerks, grinding of teeth, unsteady voice, increased muscular tone)
SOMATIC(SENSORY) (tinnitus, blurring of vision, hot and cold flashes, feelings of weakness, pricking sensation)
CARDIOVASCULAR SYMPTOMS (tachcardia, palpitations, pain in chest, throbbing of vessels, fainting feelings, sighing, dyspnea)

Section Header:
